Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.90,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这么痛苦的回忆的话 我将不再向他人渴求什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.84,0:00:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十六岁的冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.77,0:00:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我体验了能撕裂身心的痛苦离别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.28,0:01:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}白色花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.96,0:02:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又到圣诞节了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与栞的初次相遇是在春天的某一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天早晨 我比平常早了很多地来到了学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中二年级的我对什么都感到厌烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是这个宛如天使牧场的学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是带着纯真微笑的学生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界一定是正确的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.09,0:02:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就是无法适应它的坏羔羊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救这样的我吧 阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.07,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.27,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得和大家一起笑不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得去听那些毫无兴趣的话题不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我保持着沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.81,0:02:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连做什么好或是想去做什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的事情全部忘掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的内心中没有一丝的滋润
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.04,0:03:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一个人困在一片干涸的荒野中无路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.12,0:03:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着大人样的她 看起来全身充满着我所没有的滋润的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.76,0:03:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.28,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我还是第一次听到\n从你嘴里冒出别人的名字来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.07,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今早认识了一个那样的一年级生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的内心中 有什么东西正在开始变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.12,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣 你作为花蕾的自觉好像太少了一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有稀客在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.35,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为祥子长得跟日本娃娃一样漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不由自主地就想招待她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我长得一副洋味十足的脸孔真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 闹别扭了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 我喜欢圣的脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也是凭脸孔选的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她曾说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“因为我想一直看着这张脸 所以请待在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这一句话 我决定成为她的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢这样单纯而明快的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 从一开始姐姐对待我的方式就非常地高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我变得连自已都吃惊的积极起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗？ 圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞同学今天休假了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概在圣堂那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像理所当然似的栞出现在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为被这个世界所爱的洁白而闪耀的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 白蔷薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心情...会让你为难吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将自已完全地暴露 追寻着依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全不再有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.91,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直想着要见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.86,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于在这个学园里能遇见栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想从心里对神说声感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在可利用的时间里我们都尽量单独相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越远离蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.12,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断陷入了栞的那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微保持一点距离不是更好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果想认妹妹 那到也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式地交与念珠 好好地向大家介绍一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我可以走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有打算认栞作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹的仪式\n是那些没有像征就无法安心的人们做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从心底嘲笑着这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.86,0:07:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 我们双方各自都将\n与生俱来的双手连结到了同一个人的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个结果就是将其它的东西完全地排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被说了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了吗？ 游泳的补习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.19,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在事故中丧失了双亲的栞一直住在学生宿舍里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天 栞没有回到长崎的叔叔那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是留在了东京的某个修道院里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时在这里避避雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.81,0:08:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么关系 擦擦你自已的头发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.97,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.50,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们 会作为不同的个体出生到这个世上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 你再睡一会儿也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了后我会叫醒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨啊 别停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就这样停止好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想与栞溶为一体然后消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种心情究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向自已以外的人渴求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路的前方又是哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.55,0:10:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个答案恐怕永远也找不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.35,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最真实的东西只有栞的悸动 体温和吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.01,0:10:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些就是我所期望的这个世界的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.57,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的心中栞的存在膨胀得越来越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.65,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在蔷薇馆的时间变得越来越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.08,0:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也想和你一起喝喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.36,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.18,0:11:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断绝与我的姐妹之缘 重新找一个妹妹如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.65,0:11:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.71,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要违反约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.25,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我毕业以前 你可要好好地待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你不认妹妹 那也没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走你自已不会后悔的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摆出那副表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就像我是瘟神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是说教吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷静一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明对我们的事什么也不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你又知道栞同学什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“什么”是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是不要陷得太深为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特意来说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到你受伤的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她如果不在了你会怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞会...不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都没听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学毕业后会进入修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要成为修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.15,0:12:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.36,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在进入这间学校之前就已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要隐瞒到现在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没有机会说而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了也不会有什么改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然很喜欢栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却不喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个毕业前的陪伴… 你是这样随便地考虑的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这么喜欢一个人也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么要成为修女什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 你宁愿选择神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是只有栞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要抛弃我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要像那样逼问我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为修女是我的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么不敢看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在迷惑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.16,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚在看着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是栞的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输给了圣母玛莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的上课态度变得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结业式的那天 我受到传唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是栞的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.01,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她已经再没有什么关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞也是这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是自已的错之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞也被叫来这里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.46,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一头陷入一样东西中而看不清周围 不是一件很寂寞的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.43,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞两日前提出了外宿申请 无论在宿舍还是修道院都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.47,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 怎样才能见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蔷薇馆会开一个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.67,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令会为大家做好吃的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有心情的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 好想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.84,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在见不着你的时候 我只是想着你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.77,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使做祈祷 也没法让你的样子离开脑海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.37,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长非常担心我们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做过约定不再见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.93,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.93,0:15:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未知的土地上 不被任何人打扰的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.09,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和圣在一起 到哪里都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好行李就过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在车站等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞微笑着目送我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法忘记那个微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.55,0:16:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定的时间已过去3小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞已经不会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我仍无法离开月台的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.10,0:17:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法舍弃也许栞\n马上就会从那个楼梯下来的仅有的一点希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是做梦 我也想见到栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.96,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代替栞同学来接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.18,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学好像不会与你一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学好像曾经来过这个车站一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从远处注视着在月台上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后觉得果然还是不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然来了为什么不直接...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见面后会让决心变弱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变弱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她看起来很有大人样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟仍只是高中一年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会动摇也是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.97,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞会去哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听说会转学到很远的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.19,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是她接受了的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.38,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有遇见我的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够相遇是件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能创造可以坦然回想着\n“能够相遇真好”的未来 那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种未来一定无法来临的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤痕总有一天会愈合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你不是还有我在身边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.83,0:18:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是真以为我只爱着你的脸孔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.81,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.43,0:18:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失礼 那只是为了不增加你负担的一个方便的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对待你的方式可是很高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是姐姐不是就要毕业了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会担心你的可不只是我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.28,0:19:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.12,0:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是令做的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.06,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经向圣的母亲打了电话说你要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从明天开始就是开心的寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就玩到深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安安静静地闹它一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期已经变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.82,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞前夜过去 我知道自己已是十七岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.85,0:20:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.18,0:20:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人也来帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.45,0:20:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.51,0:20:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日诚子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 也就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去大波斯菊编缉部时 曾见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉前段时间失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的学生给您添了不少麻烦真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.84,0:20:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是佐藤 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.70,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 今天是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见学园长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那么 我来为您带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我知道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过去一点也没变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安的毕业生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.93,0:21:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 据说已知道香织还活着的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.31,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要在圣诞前夜去见香织的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是说香织在这里了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 去见学园长是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 是这样啊 学园长就是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么两个人在隔了这么多年后终于可以再见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.51,0:21:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联欢会要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.85,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.38,0:22:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.19,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.94,0:22:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Happy Birthday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.05,0:23:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从波折的姐妹宣言开始 终于到了现在这个时候
